---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Services - Revenue Leak Audit, Growth Blueprint, Advisory | Built on Tenth"
  description="Fixed-scope revenue audits for HVAC, roofing, and plumbing companies. Find out exactly what your marketing is producing - in dollars, in 7 days. Starting at $750."
  active="services"
>

<style>
/* ── PAGE HERO ── */
.svc-hero {
  padding: 140px 48px 96px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.svc-hero-bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504307651254-35680f356dfd?w=1600&q=60');
  background-size: cover; background-position: center 40%;
  opacity: 0.06; filter: grayscale(50%);
}
.svc-hero-overlay {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 20% 50%, rgba(0,196,154,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
              linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--bg) 0%, transparent 40%, var(--bg) 100%);
}
.svc-hero-inner {
  position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
}
.svc-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 62px);
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.svc-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--teal); }
.svc-hero-sub {
  font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.74;
  font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 520px;
}
.svc-hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* Progress steps */
.svc-steps {
  background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--rule2);
  border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px 28px;
}
.svc-steps-label {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink3); margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.svc-step-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 10px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.svc-step-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.svc-step-num {
  width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid var(--teal4);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0;
}
.svc-step-name {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); flex: 1;
}
.svc-step-price {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink2);
}
.svc-step-arrow { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--rule2); flex-shrink: 0; }

/* ── TRUST BAR ── */
.trust-bar {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  background: var(--bg2);
}
.trust-bar-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
}
.trust-item {
  padding: 28px 32px; border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  text-align: center;
}
.trust-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.trust-n {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 32px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--teal); letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.trust-l { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 300; }

/* ── SERVICE CARDS ── */
.svcs-wrap { padding: 96px 48px; }
.svcs-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }

.svc-card {
  background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
  transition: border-color 0.25s;
}
.svc-card:hover { border-color: var(--rule2); }
.svc-card.featured { border-color: rgba(0,196,154,0.3); }
.svc-card.featured:hover { border-color: rgba(0,196,154,0.55); }

.svc-card-img {
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg3), var(--bg4));
  min-height: 360px;
}
.svc-card-img img {
  width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
  filter: grayscale(25%) brightness(0.65);
  transition: transform 0.6s var(--ease), filter 0.4s;
}
.svc-card:hover .svc-card-img img { transform: scale(1.04); filter: grayscale(5%) brightness(0.75); }
.svc-card-img::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
  background: rgba(0,196,154,0.06); pointer-events: none;
}
.svc-card-img::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 2;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 60%, var(--bg2) 100%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.svc-card-body { padding: 44px 48px 44px 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.svc-tier {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink3); margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.svc-tier.ft { color: var(--teal); }
.svc-name {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.svc-price {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 44px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1; margin: 14px 0 6px; color: var(--ink);
}
.svc-delivery {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--ink3);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.svc-pitch {
  font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.72; font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 28px; border-left: 2px solid var(--teal4); padding-left: 16px;
}
.svc-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--rule); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.svc-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 32px; flex: 1; }
.svc-features li {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
  font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.55; font-weight: 300;
}
.sf-arrow { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 8px; }

/* Sample findings panel inside card */
.findings-panel {
  background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 5px; padding: 18px 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.fp-label {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink3); margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.fp-rows { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
.fp-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.fp-key { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink2); font-weight: 300; }
.fp-val { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); white-space: nowrap; }
.fp-val.bad { color: var(--neg); }
.fp-val.ok  { color: var(--pos); }

/* Timeline panel (for advisory) */
.timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.tl-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.tl-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.tl-week {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--teal); white-space: nowrap; min-width: 72px;
}
.tl-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink2); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.5; }

/* ── DIFFERENTIATOR SECTION ── */
.diff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--rule); border: 1px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 48px; }
.diff-card { background: var(--bg2); padding: 32px 30px; transition: background 0.25s; }
.diff-card:hover { background: var(--bg3); }
.diff-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.diff-title { font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--ink); }
.diff-body { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; }

/* ── FAQ ── */
.faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-top: 48px; }
.faq-item {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); overflow: hidden;
}
.faq-q {
  width: 100%; background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px;
  padding: 22px 0; text-align: left;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink);
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.faq-q:hover { color: var(--teal); }
.faq-chevron {
  width: 20px; height: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--rule2); border-radius: 3px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink3);
  transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.2s;
}
.faq-item.open .faq-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); border-color: var(--teal4); color: var(--teal); }
.faq-a {
  font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 300;
  max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s var(--ease), padding 0.3s;
  padding: 0 0 0 0;
}
.faq-item.open .faq-a { max-height: 400px; padding-bottom: 20px; }

/* ── BOTTOM CTA ── */
.bottom-cta {
  text-align: center; padding: 112px 48px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.bottom-cta-glow {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(0,196,154,0.07) 0%, transparent 65%);
}
.bottom-cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto; }
.bottom-cta h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 52px); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 18px; }
.bottom-cta h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--teal); }
.bottom-cta p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.72; margin-bottom: 36px; font-weight: 300; }
.bottom-cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 1100px) {
  .svc-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
}
@media (max-width: 960px) {
  .svc-hero { padding: 100px 20px 60px; }
  .svc-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 8vw, 44px); }
  .svc-hero-ctas { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .svc-hero-ctas a { justify-content: center; }
  .svcs-wrap { padding: 56px 20px; }
  .svc-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .svc-card-img { min-height: 180px; }
  .svc-card-img::after { background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 40%, var(--bg2) 100%); }
  .svc-card-body { padding: 24px 20px; }
  .svc-price { font-size: 40px; }
  .trust-bar-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .trust-item:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
  .trust-item:nth-child(1), .trust-item:nth-child(2) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .trust-n { font-size: 26px; }
  .diff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .faq-list { margin-top: 32px; }
  .bottom-cta { padding: 72px 20px; }
  .bottom-cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .bottom-cta-buttons a { justify-content: center; }
  /* Two-column section divs inline styles */
  .inner > div[style],
  .inner > [style*="grid-template-columns"] {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    gap: 20px !important;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .trust-bar-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .trust-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .trust-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .findings-panel { padding: 14px 16px; }
  .fp-label { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .fp-rows { gap: 0; }
  .fp-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226,221,208,0.06);
  }
  .fp-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
  .fp-key {
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .fp-val {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    line-height: 1.35;
    white-space: normal;
    text-align: right;
    max-width: 150px;
  }
  .timeline { gap: 0; }
}
</style>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="svc-hero">
  <div class="svc-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="svc-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="svc-hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="dispatch-label">For HVAC, Roofing &amp; Plumbing Companies</div>
      <h1>Your marketing is spending money.<br><em>Find out if it's booking jobs.</em></h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-sub">Most HVAC, roofing, and plumbing companies spend $5K–$15K a month and can't tell you which dollar produced a booked job. We can show you that in writing, in 7 days, without a single call.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas">
        <a href="/apply" class="cta-primary">Get a Revenue Leak Audit</a>
        <a href="#audit" class="cta-secondary">See What's Included</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-steps">
      <div class="svc-steps-label">Three ways to work together</div>
      <div class="svc-step-row">
        <div class="svc-step-num">01</div>
        <div class="svc-step-name">Revenue Leak Audit</div>
        <div class="svc-step-price">$750</div>
        <div class="svc-step-arrow"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-step-row">
        <div class="svc-step-num">02</div>
        <div class="svc-step-name">Growth System Blueprint</div>
        <div class="svc-step-price">$3,000</div>
        <div class="svc-step-arrow"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-step-row">
        <div class="svc-step-num">03</div>
        <div class="svc-step-name">90-Day Growth Advisory</div>
        <div class="svc-step-price">$7,500</div>
        <div class="svc-step-arrow"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TRUST BAR -->
<div class="trust-bar">
  <div class="trust-bar-inner">
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-n">$0</div>
      <div class="trust-l">incentive to recommend<br>more ad spend, ever</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-n">7</div>
      <div class="trust-l">business days to full<br>audit delivery</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-n">$100K+</div>
      <div class="trust-l">average annual leakage<br>found per audit</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-n">100%</div>
      <div class="trust-l">written delivery,<br>no calls required</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SERVICE CARDS -->
<div class="svcs-wrap">
  <div class="svcs-inner">

    <!-- AUDIT -->
    <div class="svc-card reveal" id="audit">
      <div class="svc-card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?w=700&q=75" alt="Revenue audit report" loading="lazy" onerror="this.setAttribute('data-failed','1')" />
        <div class="img-fb">📄</div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card-body">
        <div class="svc-tier">Start Here</div>
        <div class="svc-name">Revenue Leak Audit</div>
        <div class="svc-price">$750</div>
        <div class="svc-delivery">Delivered in 7 business days · No calls required · Everything in writing</div>
        <p class="svc-pitch">
          You've been writing checks every month. Your agency sends reports you can't connect to booked jobs. We'll show you the real picture, benchmarked against your top competitors, with every gap turned into an annual dollar figure.
        </p>
        <div class="findings-panel">
          <div class="fp-label">Sample findings for a $2.3M HVAC company</div>
          <div class="fp-rows">
            <div class="fp-row"><span class="fp-key">Phone answer rate</span><span class="fp-val bad">66%, losing ~$84K/yr</span></div>
            <div class="fp-row"><span class="fp-key">Google Ads tracking</span><span class="fp-val bad">Not installed, $4,200/mo blind</span></div>
            <div class="fp-row"><span class="fp-key">Estimate follow-up</span><span class="fp-val bad">None, 68% of quotes go cold</span></div>
            <div class="fp-row"><span class="fp-key">Google reviews</span><span class="fp-val ok">4.8 stars · 127 reviews</span></div>
            <div class="fp-row"><span class="fp-key">Total annual leakage</span><span class="fp-val bad">$247,000 identified</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-divider"></div>
        <ul class="svc-features">
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Google Business Profile benchmarked against 5–7 top competitors in your market</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Every marketing channel assessed: which ones are booking jobs, which are burning cash</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Phone system analysis: answer rate, booking rate, revenue leaking through missed calls</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Website conversion audit: mobile speed, phone number placement, trust signals, CTAs</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Every gap translated into annual revenue impact, not "needs improvement," but specific dollars</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Prioritized action list: what to fix first, what it's worth, who does it</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/apply?service=audit" class="cta-primary" style="align-self:flex-start">Start My Audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BLUEPRINT -->
    <div class="svc-card featured reveal" id="blueprint">
      <div class="svc-card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531973576160-7125cd663d86?w=700&q=75" alt="Growth system blueprint" loading="lazy" onerror="this.setAttribute('data-failed','1')" />
        <div class="img-fb">📐</div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card-body">
        <div class="svc-tier ft">Then Build the System · Most Popular</div>
        <div class="svc-name">Growth System Blueprint</div>
        <div class="svc-price">$3,000</div>
        <div class="svc-delivery">2–3 week delivery · Includes full audit · No calls required</div>
        <p class="svc-pitch">
          Most owners who get an audit know exactly what needs fixing, but 90 days later nothing has changed because there's no time to build the system. The blueprint is that system, already built. Scripts written. Sequences built. Dashboard set up. Your office manager runs it Monday.
        </p>
        <div class="svc-divider"></div>
        <ul class="svc-features">
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Full Revenue Leak Audit included, everything in the $750 engagement</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Word-for-word phone script for your front desk, handles pricing questions, tire kickers, the works</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>5-touch estimate follow-up sequence by text and email, recovers $40K–$80K/year for most shops</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Weekly dashboard: cost per booked job by channel, built in Google Sheets, takes 10 minutes</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Channel strategy: exactly where to move budget, with a 90-day reallocation plan</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>90-day implementation calendar with specific weekly actions, no guesswork</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>5–8 ready-to-use templates: scripts, sequences, tracking sheets</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/apply?service=blueprint" class="cta-primary" style="align-self:flex-start">Apply for a Blueprint</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ADVISORY -->
    <div class="svc-card reveal" id="advisory">
      <div class="svc-card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?w=700&q=75" alt="90-day advisory - weekly written number reviews" loading="lazy" onerror="this.setAttribute('data-failed','1')" />
        <div class="img-fb">🤝</div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card-body">
        <div class="svc-tier">Then Improve It</div>
        <div class="svc-name">90-Day Growth Advisory</div>
        <div class="svc-price">$7,500</div>
        <div class="svc-delivery">12-week engagement · Includes audit + blueprint · No calls required</div>
        <p class="svc-pitch">
          Building the system is one thing. Making it work in your actual business, with your team, your market, and your busy season, is another. The advisory is for owners who want someone reviewing what's happening every week and telling them exactly what to adjust.
        </p>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-week">Weeks 1–2</span><span class="tl-desc">Audit + Blueprint delivered. Quick wins identified and handed off.</span></div>
          <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-week">Weeks 3–4</span><span class="tl-desc">First changes implemented. Phone script live. Tracking dashboard running.</span></div>
          <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-week">Weeks 5–8</span><span class="tl-desc">Weekly written review: what's working, what to adjust, what to stop.</span></div>
          <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-week">Weeks 9–12</span><span class="tl-desc">Measuring, iterating, monthly competitor re-benchmarking.</span></div>
          <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-week">On exit</span><span class="tl-desc">Before/after in dollars. 6-month roadmap. Everything documented.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-divider"></div>
        <ul class="svc-features">
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Full audit + blueprint in week 1, so you're not waiting 12 weeks to start</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Weekly written performance review: numbers, interpretation, specific next action</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Questions answered in writing within 24–48 hours, every week for 90 days</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Monthly competitor re-benchmarking to track the gap closing in real time</li>
          <li><span class="sf-arrow"></span>Exit report showing exactly what changed, in dollars, over the full 90 days</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/apply?service=advisory" class="cta-primary" style="align-self:flex-start">Apply for Advisory</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- DIFFERENTIATORS -->
<div class="wrap alt">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="rule-label"><span class="section-tag">Why This Is Different</span></div>
